I"è<p>The fourth JLESC Summer School will be held at NCSA from July 20 to 21, 2017, following the <a href="/events/7th-jlesc-workshop">7th JLESC Worksphop</a>.</p>

<p>The summer school will feature two days of talks on topics like Python, MPI, OpenACC and more.
The school is offered to students (mainly PhD students and post-docs) of the collaboration and open
to students and faculties outside of the collaboration, if room.</p>

<p>See <a href="http://www.ncsa.illinois.edu/Conferences/JLESCsummer17/">here</a> for more information. The <a href="http://www.ncsa.illinois.edu/Conferences/JLESCsummer17/program.html">program</a> is now also available!</p>
